subject: Track and Field
lead_paragraph: Ivan Ukhov held off Jaroslav Baba to win the high jump, and Anna Avdeyeva narrowly beat Christina Schwanitz in the shot-put as Russia increased its medal tally at the European indoor championships in Paris on Saturday.
